cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with measuring and understanding online behavioural advertising, which involves the use of algorithms and data analysis techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), or Multimedia (cs.MM). Among these, cs.CY and cs.CR are the most likely categories as they deal with privacy concerns and regulation in online advertising. cs.SI and cs.IR are also likely categories as they deal with data analysis and online behaviour. cs.MM is the least likely category as it is not directly related to the topic of the paper.
